### Description

Have this code that checks the PostNotifications permission status -
```csharp
public async Task<bool> HasPushNotificationPermission()
{
	PermissionStatus status = await Permissions.CheckStatusAsync<Permissions.PostNotifications>();
	return status == PermissionStatus.Granted;
}
```

The status is always `Granted`, even on a fresh install of the app, with 'Allow notifications' set to false


